extendedInfo.description: Have you ever wanted to check the meaning of your dream from your bedroom? Is your computer taking too long to boot up? This won't be a problem any longer... Download this Dream Dictionary today and learn more about your dreams.You will have this application always with you, whenever you go. Checking dream meanings during your holidays could not be easier!Really easy to use application, you can browse through the keywords or use the intelligent search facility. Give it a go.If you like it, PLEASE review it. Thanks in advance.You can also âLikeâ our Facebook page.http://www.facebook.com/dreammeaning

reviews.title: Awesome
reviews.comment: I remember a lot of the details in most of my dreams yet they still didn\'t make sense. I found this app and typed in a few of the things I remembered and it all completely made sense. I love it!
reviews.author: Lydia Ochoa

reviews.title: Amazing
reviews.comment: This app is phenomenal and accurate, providing in-depth descriptions of what your dreams mean and how they may effect you. I have used this app on more than one occasion, either with purpose and motive or just being curious. Definitely worth downloading.
reviews.author: Katie Kane

reviews.title: Good fun!
reviews.comment: I have vivid dreams often and this hits close to home for what is going on in reality. Something I can share with friends and family.

reviews.comment: pretty cool. seems very blunt and detailed. but very accurate in my experience

reviews.title: Pretty terrible....
reviews.comment: I\'ve been interpreting dreams for years, and am always looking for good books and apps to help guide me, but this is just terribly mediocre. If you\'re a preteen, you might enjoy this. Otherwise, keep searching. I guess I\'ll stick to my books until I find a good app. Thanks anyways, had to uninstall.
